room_title: Escape room "The Jungle Jr." by Sherlock's Escape Rooms in Florence (KY)
room_description: While you and your friends are exploring the jungle, you come across the tree of life and see that it is quickly fading away! You must help! The magical jungle crystal is missing and must be returned to restore life to the tree. Find the clues within the jungle and return the crystal before the sun sets! Good luck, explorers!
